[This area in Western Province has been afflicted before in recent years.
Cultures have shown that they were part of the Kruger-Mozambique-Zambia
strain. We will gladly fingerprint check isolates from this series of
outbreaks. Please contact me directly at mehj2020@vt8200.vetmed.lsu.edu.
